georgia,serif;margin:0 50px 15px;color:#666" class=3D"css-14jlz04"><span>He=
 refills his tanks about every four days, and the =E2=80=9Crack price=E2=80=
=9D that his wholesale gasoline provider charges jumped to $3.347 per gallo=
n last week from $2.398 on Feb. 25 =E2=80=94 an increase of 39.6 percent. H=
is last truckload cost $39,488.</span></p><p style=3D"font:normal 17px/25px=
 georgia,serif;color:#333;margin:20px 0 15px"><span>Weatherall raised </spa=
n><span style=3D"font-style:italic">his </span><span>price by only 33.8 per=
cent: =E2=80=9CHe would charge more, but he feared losing business if his c=
ompetitors did not follow,=E2=80=9D Lydia wrote. =E2=80=9CFewer visits also=
 mean lower sales at his convenience store and restaurant.=E2=80=9D</span><=
/p><p style=3D"font:normal 17px/25px georgia,serif;color:#333;margin:0 0 15=
